day15: [{"id": 1, "name": "Revolutionary Patriot Burger", "price": 18.0, "cost_price": 9.0, "description": "Now even bolder, our Patriot Burger is loaded with jalapeno cheddar, crispy onions, smoky chipotle sauce, and a special blend of spices, served with our seasoned fries."}, {"id": 2, "name": "Smokey Mountain BBQ Ribs", "price": 19.0, "cost_price": 9.5, "description": "These ribs are marinated in a robust blend of spices before being slow-cooked and glazed in a Smokey Mountain-style molasses BBQ sauce, served with spicy loaded baked potatoes and apple slaw."}, {"id": 5, "name": "Bourbon Bliss Apple Pie", "price": 13.0, "cost_price": 6.5, "description": "A richer bourbon infusion elevates our apple pie, with cinnamon-spiced apples and vanilla bean ice cream, crowned with a crunchy caramel pecan topping."}, {"id": 25, "name": "Signature Farm-to-Table Special", "price": 20.0, "cost_price": 10.0, "description": "Seasonal local produce stars in this ever-changing special, featuring the best of what our regional farms have to offer, paired with a unique house-made sauce."}]
